short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When there is a lot of webpage content to browse, this extension can quickly go to the bottom of the webpage with one click.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
When we browse the webpage, we often encounter pages that are particularly long.

If you want to reach the bottom of the page quickly, it takes a long time. 

This extension can help you quickly reach the bottom of the page and save time.
